---
import talvez from "../assets/talvez.webp";
import FadeIn from "./fade-in";
---

<section
  class="relative min-h-[680px] overflow-hidden bg-neutral-900 px-6 py-20 text-center text-white md:min-h-[720px] md:px-10 md:py-24"
>
  <img
    src={talvez.src}
    alt="Persona pensando en síntomas de bienestar metabólico y hormonal"
    class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full object-cover object-[62%_center]"
    loading="lazy"
  />
  <div
    class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-r from-black/35 via-black/10 to-transparent md:hidden"
    aria-hidden="true"
  >
  </div>

  <div
    class="relative z-10 mx-auto flex max-w-7xl justify-center md:justify-start"
  >
    <div class="max-w-2xl text-center md:w-1/2">
      <FadeIn
        client:visible
        as="h2"
        className="font-sans text-xl leading-tight font-medium text-white uppercase text-shadow-md/10 md:text-2xl"
      >
        Tal vez te está pasando esto:
      </FadeIn>

      <FadeIn
        client:visible
        as="div"
        className="mt-10 text-lg leading-8 text-white text-shadow-md/10 md:text-2xl md:leading-10"
        delay={0.1}
      >
        <p>
          Te cuesta bajar de peso aunque “comes bien”<br />
          Te sientes cansada(o) sin razón alguna<br />
          Tu ciclo es irregular o doloroso<br />
          Te ha costado embarazarte<br />
          Tienes ansiedad por azúcar o carbohidratos<br />
          Sientes que tu cuerpo cambió... y no sabes por qué
        </p>

        <p class="mt-10 font-medium">
          No es normal. Y no tienes que vivir así.
        </p>
      </FadeIn>

      <FadeIn client:visible className="mt-10" delay={0.2}>
        <a
          href="/contacto"
          class="group inline-flex min-w-64 items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-linear-to-r from-[#31ADD0] via-[#8FC746] to-[#31ADD0] bg-size-[200%_100%] bg-position-[0%_50%] py-1.5 pr-4 pl-5 font-sans text-lg font-medium text-white shadow-lg shadow-[#31ADD0]/20 transition-[background-position,box-shadow] duration-500 ease-out hover:bg-position-[100%_50%] hover:shadow-[#8FC746]/30"
        >
          <span>AGENDA TU CITA AHORA</span>
          <svg
            class="size-5 shrink-0 transition-transform duration-300 ease-out group-hover:translate-x-0.5 group-hover:-translate-y-0.5"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            aria-hidden="true"
          >
            <path d="M7 17 17 7"></path>
            <path d="M8 7h9v9"></path>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </FadeIn>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
